description: Try our easy to follow Gluten-free Sausage Skewers recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Skewer & kebab,Sausage,Seafood free,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Mushroom,Zucchini,Soy free,Wheat free,Pork,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Gluten-free Sausage Skewers Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 6 pork gluten-free sausages, standard sausages can be used

recipeInstructions.text: You will need 8 soaked bamboo skewers.
Cut 6 pork and veal with sage and onion gluten-free sausages into thirds.
Cut a red capsicum into large pieces then dice and cut a red onion into 8 wedges.
Thread onto skewers with sausage pieces, button mushrooms and thick slices of zucchini.
Cook on a preheated barbecue or chargrill pan for 8 minutes, turning frequently until cooked through.
Serve with purchased tomato relish and a green salad.
